<SLUG> BC-Israel-Palestinians,0308 </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
Palestinians demand Israeli compliance with peace pact
</HEADLINE>
 &UR; By NASSER SHIYOUKHI &QC; 
 &UR; Associated Press Writer &QC; 

<TEXT>
