	   SYDNEY, Australia _ An Australian-U.S. team is readying for its
shot at the first nonstop around-the-world balloon flight, with
liftoff planned for just days after Chicago millionaire Steve
Fossett's team splashed down in the Pacific Ocean.
AUSTRALIA-BALLOON QUEST. Expected by 0300 GMT; launch tentatively
