 &UR; SOCCER:
	   SAO PAULO, Brazil _ Palmeiras beats a tired Cruzeiro 3-1
Saturday, forcing a third and decisive game in the first Mercosur
Cup championship final before a partisan crowd at Parque Antartica
stadium.
	   Slug Sports-Soccer-Copa Mercosur-Cruzeiro-Palmeiras. Has moved.
	   By Jack Epstein.
